      "text": "Let $d_n=p_{n+1}-p_n$, where $p_n$ denotes the $n$th prime. Is it true that\\[\\frac{\\max_{n<x}d_{n}d_{n-1}}{(\\max_{n<x}d_n)^2}\\to 0\\]as $x\\to \\infty$?"
